column2:
"... This spot alone is completely different.
There's no signs he even tried to hide that he was doing research."

"Over there... what was he making?
Or possibly, he was attaching something."

"It seems like something
that tasteless Luther would do."

"Wonderful, I can't say that it's complete,
but there is data left behind."
"This is a walk in the park..."

"Record of merging D-arkers & Primitive
Organisms. Of course, he was combinin
them...There certainly had to be a reaction."
"But it seems that's not all..."
"... What is this?"

"Analysis of water composition, synthesis with stars...
was he tampering with the planets themselves?"

"This guy....
what is he planning."

"Ah, oh.... sorry.
I'm not even sure myself."

"Whatever Luther's trying to do,
it's bigger than I ever imagined.
That is all that I know."

"... Let's go back.
If Xiao sees our current data,
he'll understand in more detail."

"A new kind of hostile!?
Ugh, we have to defeat it...!"

"……ここだけは、完全に異質ね。
研究していたことを隠す気もない。"

"あそこで……何かを作ってた？
あるいは、くっつけてたのかな。"

"悪趣味なルーサーの
やりそうなことね。"

"よし、完全とは言えないけど
データが残ってるわ。"
"ちょちょいのちょい、っと……"

"ダーカーと原生種の混合記録……
……やっぱり、混ぜてるのか。
道理で反応があるはずよ。"
"でも、これだけじゃないはず……"

"水の組成分解、星との合成……
……惑星自体をいじくってる？"

"ちょっと、アイツ
……何を考えてるの。"

"あ、ああ……ごめん。
あたしにも、わけがわからないの。"

"ただ、ルーサーのやろうとしてることは
あたしの考えている以上にやばい。
それだけは、わかった。"

"……戻りましょう。
今のデータ、シャオが見れば
もっと細かいことがわかるはず。"

"新手のエネミー！？
くっ、倒すしかない……！"
